                    "title": "Are You Out There?",
                    "author": "Collen Durril",
                    "generation": 0,
                    "pages": [
                      {
                        "raw": "{\"text\":\"My name is Collen Durril. This message is to whoever might be able to find it. Presently in Eastglade as I send this, chesting North. My father and I have been on the run for three weeks. We are in need of immediate assistance.\",\"color\":\"gray\",\"italic\":false}"
                      },
                      {
                        "raw": "{\"text\":\"Something happened in Sovscell, and nobody knows what it was just yet. All we know is that we were nearly killed, and that we've not been back since. I've created multiple messages for whoever might find them at this point, and I have no idea if any of them have been found.\",\"color\":\"gray\",\"italic\":false}"
                      },
                      {
                        "raw": "{\"text\":\"If you find this, you must listen carefully. Don't go to the city. Come find us. I can guarantee we need each other's help. We will remain north of the city. We are good hunters, we can provide for you and teach you our skills.\",\"color\":\"gray\",\"italic\":false}"
                      },
                      {
                        "raw": "{\"text\":\"Good luck. May Benevolence have mercy upon us.\",\"color\":\"gray\",\"italic\":false}"
                      }
                    ],
                    "resolved": false
                  }
                }
              }
            ]
          }
